<h2 class="western" style="margin-top: 0.11in; margin-bottom: 0.5in"><a name="__RefHeading__4364_2146186683"></a><a name="_Toc464563319"></a>
3.2<font face="宋体"><span lang="zh-CN">公共函数</span></font></h2>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
--<font face="宋体"><span lang="zh-CN">输出</span></font>table<font face="宋体"><span lang="zh-CN">数组所有元素</span></font></p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
function Unpack(t,i)</p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
   i = i or 1</p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
   if t[i] then</p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
     return t[i],Unpack(t,i+1)</p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
   end</p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
end</p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
<br/>
<br/>

</p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
--<font face="宋体"><span lang="zh-CN">检测一个表是否为空表</span></font></p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
function TableIsEmpty(t)</p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
	return _G.next(t) == nil</p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
end</p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
<br/>
<br/>

</p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
--<font face="宋体"><span lang="zh-CN">检测一个表是否为非空表</span></font></p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
function TableIsNotEmpty(t)</p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
    return false == TableIsEmpty(t)</p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
end</p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
<br/>
<br/>

</p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
--<font face="宋体"><span lang="zh-CN">输出日志信息</span></font></p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
--aKey <font face="宋体"><span lang="zh-CN">输入日志类型
字符串或数字</span></font></p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
--bLength <font face="宋体"><span lang="zh-CN">打印输出信息的长度</span></font></p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
--cValue <font face="宋体"><span lang="zh-CN">待输出的信息，字符串类型就是一串字符串，数字类型就是数组</span></font></p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
function LogPrint(aKey,bLength,cValue)</p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
	assert(bLength &gt;= 1,&quot;LogPrint bLength invlaid&quot;)</p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
	if(aKey == LOG_TYPE.ENUM_STRING) then  
</p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
      assert(type(cValue) == &quot;string&quot;,&quot;LogPrint cValue
invlaid0&quot;)</p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
	elseif(aKey == LOG_TYPE.ENUM_NUMBER)	 then	   
</p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
	    assert(TableIsNotEmpty(cValue),&quot;LogPrint cValue invlaid1&quot;)</p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
	else</p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
	    error(&quot;LogPrint aKey invlaid&quot;) 
</p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
	end	</p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
<br/>
<br/>

</p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
	local logTable = {</p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
		key = LOG_TYPE.ENUM_STRING,  
</p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
		length = 0,             
</p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
		value = nil             
</p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
    }</p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
	logTable.key = aKey 
</p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
	logTable.length = bLength		</p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
	logTable.value = cValue</p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
	mylib.LogPrint(logTable)</p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
end</p>
<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">

<p class="western" style="margin-top: 0.19in; margin-bottom: 0.19in; line-height: 100%">
